replies.body:
For me it's often more like: 

Ok, you could have done that.  And, this guy could have done that.  And, oh, he could have done this.  Time for me to place my ward.  Ok, he could have done that.  Why didn't he do this?  Time to hit my heal button.  He could have done that....

{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}
